de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jconfiguration.rest

Class RestConfigurator.EmailConfigJaxBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jconfiguration.rest.RestConfigurator.EmailConfigJaxBean
  • Enclosing class:
    RestConfigurator

    public static class RestConfigurator.EmailConfigJaxBean
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a data class for the email configuration. It is used by Jersey to deserialize JSON. Also it can be used for tests to provide the correct contents. This class in particular is used by the POST for the email configuration. See the RestConfigurator.updateEmailConfiguration(int, EmailConfigJaxBean) updateEmailConfiguration} method for more information.
